name: agg-regrid
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "agg-regrid" %}
{% set version = "0.2.2" %}
{% set sha256 = "9aac13e714b7375481ea424f051951edf21897d933b6b3b01822796ea0fdf2ab" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/SciTools-incubator/iris-{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 1001
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
    - cython
    - numpy
  run:
    - python
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - iris

test:
  imports:
    - agg_regrid

about:
  home: https://github.com/SciTools-incubator/iris-{{ name }}
  license: LGPL-3.0
  license_family: LGPL
  license_file: COPYING.LESSER
  summary: "A conservative area-weighted regridder that uses AGG to rasterise a source iris cube to a target grid"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bjlittle
    - pelson
    - cpelley
